## Blocking Comment Sites
\.+(spot.im|disqus.com|livefyre.com)$

## White Listing TLDs
## Reject TLDs that don't match
^(?!.*(com|net|org|us|co|edu|mil|gov|biz|info|xyz|ly)$)

